{"id":151669,"name":"Twitch Chat Minimal Badges","description":"Requires \u003ca href=\"http://frankerfacez.com\"\u003eFrankerFaceZ\u003c/a\u003e. The CSS selectors used in this stylish are mostly added in by this extension.\r\n\r\nThe default colors for this stylish are intended to be used with Dark Mode on Twitch. If you are using the default Light Mode on Twitch you may want to change them.\r\n\r\nRemoves all but four Twitch Chat Badges. Badges are displayed as a four pixel border at the left side of the Chat Line spanning 100% of the height (one pixel is taken off so consecutive lines that have badges don't blend together).\r\nThe following are the Badges still shown:\r\n\u003cul\u003e\r\n\u003cli\u003eTwitch Staff\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003cli\u003eGlobal Moderator\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003cli\u003eBroadcaster\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003cli\u003eModerator\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003c/ul\u003e\r\n\r\nChat Messages are formatted to be aligned with the Nick. So messages that are long enough to create a second line will not go under the timestamp if you are using them. Timestamps are fixed to be right aligned.","user":{"id":216229,"name":"Jimmie1717","email":"jimmie1717@gmail.com","paypal_email":null,"homepage":"http://zeldacodes.org/","about":null,"license":"ccbysa"},"updated":"2018-08-18T10:54:14.000Z","weekly_install_count":0,"total_install_count":219,"rating":null,"after_screenshot_name":"https://userstyles.org/style_screenshots/151669_after.png?r=1685692814","obsoleting_style_id":null,"obsoleting_style_name":null,"obsolete":0,"admin_delete_reason_id":null,"obsoletion_message":null,"screenshots":null,"license":"ccbysa","created":"2017-11-20T22:39:10.000Z","category":"site","raw_subcategory":"twitch","subcategory":"twitch","additional_info":"\u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003ccode\u003eI only use Google Chrome so if there are issues with Firefox they aren't going to be fixed.\u003c/code\u003e\r\n\u003cbr/\u003e\r\n\u003cb\u003eInstallation\u003c/b\u003e\r\n\u003cul\u003e\r\n\u003cli\u003eThere are optional settings to remove the \"\u0026lt;name\u0026gt; has subscribed!\" from the chat as well as the Cheer emotes/icons from chat. \u003ci\u003eBy default this is set to \u003cb\u003enot\u003c/b\u003e be used.\u003c/i\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003cli\u003eIf using forced colors you can set what color you want with the respective color option for it. Otherwise they will not be used. \u003ci\u003eBy default this is set to \u003cb\u003enot\u003c/b\u003e be used.\u003c/i\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003cli\u003eBy default timestamps are set as being used on Twitch, if you are not using them change the option.\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003c/ul\u003e\r\n\r\n\u003cb\u003eJanuary 18th, 2018:\u003c/b\u003e\r\n\u003cul\u003e\r\n\u003cli\u003eFixed badges showing a background image.\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003c/ul\u003e\r\n\u003cb\u003eNovember 29, 2017:\u003c/b\u003e\r\n\u003cul\u003e\r\n\u003cli\u003eAdded an option to remove the \"Try Prime\" and Prime Loot buttons from the main navigation.\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003c/ul\u003e\r\n\u003cb\u003eNovember 28, 2017:\u003c/b\u003e\r\n\u003cul\u003e\r\n\u003cli\u003eFixed shown badges background color. A Twitch/FrankerFaceZ update was setting them to have a color.\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003c/ul\u003e\r\n\u003cb\u003eNovember 25, 2017:\u003c/b\u003e\r\n\u003cul\u003e\r\n\u003cli\u003eAdded a Hide Stats option. Lets you hide some of the stats seen on a Twitch stream page.\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003c/ul\u003e\r\n\u003cb\u003eNovember 23, 2017:\u003c/b\u003e\r\n\u003cul\u003e\r\n\u003cli\u003eAdded the stylish name into the chat welcome message.\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003cli\u003eAdded a fix to remove a second \"Welcome to the Chat!\" message. I seem to get this rather often lately.\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003c/ul\u003e\r\n\u003cb\u003eNovember 20, 2017:\u003c/b\u003e\r\n\u003cul\u003e\r\n\u003cli\u003eI've yet to see a Twitch Staff or Twitch Administrator message in a chat. I'll update this if I find out they are different than what I have set.\u003c/li\u003e\r\n\u003c/ul\u003e","style_tags":[],"css":"@-moz-document domain(\"twitch.tv\") {\r\n\r\ndiv[data-a-target=\"chat-welcome-message\"]:before {\r\n\tdisplay: block!important;\r\n\tcontent: \"Twitch Chat Minimal Badges v1.1\";\t\r\n}\r\n\r\ndiv[data-a-target=\"chat-welcome-message\"]:nth-of-type(2) {\r\n\tdisplay: none!important;\t\r\n}\r\n\r\n/*[[hidePrime]]*/\r\n\r\n/*[[hideStats]]*/\r\n\r\n/*[[chatlineAltColor]]*/\r\n\r\n.chat-line__message {\r\n\tposition: relative;\r\n\tpadding: 5px 5px 5px /*[[timestamp]]*/!important;\r\n\tmin-height: 30px;\r\n}\r\n\r\n.chat-line__timestamp {\r\n\tposition: absolute;\r\n\tleft: 6px;\r\n\tmargin: 0;\r\n\twidth: 31px;\r\n\ttext-align: right;\r\n}\r\n\r\n.chat-line__message--badges {\r\n\tposition: absolute;\r\n\ttop: 0px;\r\n\tleft: 0;\r\n\tmin-width: /*[[timestamp]]*/;\r\n\twidth: /*[[timestamp]]*/;\r\n\theight: 100%;\r\n}\r\n.ffz-badge[data-replaced=\"2\"] {\r\n\tbackground: none!important;\r\n\tbackground-image: none!important;\r\n}\r\n[data-badge] {\r\n\tposition: absolute;\r\n\tmin-width: /*[[timestamp]]*/;\r\n\twidth: /*[[timestamp]]*/;\r\n\theight: calc(100% - 1px);\r\n\tbackground: none!important;\r\n\tbackground-image: none!important;\r\n\tdisplay: none!important;\r\n}\r\n[data-badge=\"staff\"] {\r\n\tborder-left: 4px solid /*[[staffColor]]*/!important;\r\n\tdisplay: block!important;\t\r\n}\r\n[data-badge=\"admin\"], [data-badge=\"administrator\"] {\r\n\tborder-left: 4px solid /*[[administratorColor]]*/!important;\r\n\tdisplay: block!important;\t\r\n}\r\n[data-badge=\"broadcaster\"] {\r\n\tborder-left: 4px solid /*[[broadcasterColor]]*/!important;\r\n\tdisplay: block!important;\t\r\n}\r\n[data-badge=\"moderator\"] {\r\n\tborder-left: 4px solid /*[[moderatorColor]]*/!important;\r\n\tdisplay: block!important;\t\r\n}\r\n\r\n/*[[forceNickColor]]*/\r\n\r\n/*[[forceMeColor]]*/\r\n\r\n/*[[forceMessageColor]]*/\r\n  \r\n/*[[hideSubscriber]]*/\r\n  \r\n/*[[hideCheer]]*/\r\n\r\n}","discussions":[],"discussionsCount":0